deck: Part two of the epic duel between Yuma and Shark is underway. As Shark gains the upper hand in the duel, Yuma get's a visitor from another dimension; and his name is Astral.
name: "My name is Astral"

deck: Zorin Blitz begins her assault on the Hellsing mansion. Seras Victoria and Pip Bernadotte intend to stop her, at any cost.
description: The Vatican’s formidable combat unit is mobilized in preparation for battle. Back in the heart of London, the Hellsing Mansion is attacked, and the Wild Geese represent the last line of defense against the undead.
name: Hellsing VI

deck: The battle rages on, and hope is all but lost. Zorin Blitz forces Seras to relive her childhood trauma.
description: When her memories are violated, Seras becomes trapped in an illusion which forces her to relive the most horrifying moments of her life. Upon waking from the nightmare, the real pain begins as the battle nears its end.
name: Hellsing VII

deck: Enrico Maxwell orders Iscariot to begin killing Millennium forces, as well as wiping out all civilians in the area as part of the "Ninth Crusade," much to Alexander Anderson's anger. Alucard returns.
description: The harrowing conclusion to Hellsing Ultimate features the epic return of Arucard - and Integra’s willingness to unleash his true power on their enemies!
name: Hellsing VIII

deck: Alucard, at full power, faces off against Alexander Anderson. Alucard and Integra are betrayed by a friend.
description: Arucard, gravely injured, recalls his painful childhood, his supernatural transformation, and violent and bloody altercation with Walter.
name: Hellsing IX

deck: Integra faces the Major, Seras faces the Captain, and Alucard faces Walter. The Major's true goal is revealed.
description: Shocking revelations and epic bloodlettings highlight this harrowing final chapter in the Hellsing Ultimate Saga. Find out what becomes of Arucard and the rest of the supernatural freak show!
name: Hellsing X

deck: Yuma discovers Astral is here to stay, as he duel his school teacher who is possessed by a "Numbers" a mysterious card who's originnate from the Astral World and is tied to Astral's memories.
name: " To summarize, It's an incident!!"
The True Adventures of Roody Kazootie

deck: Alucard rescues a police girl from a vampire attack, but ends up turning her into a vampire to save her.
description: Policewoman Seras Victoria is mortally wounded in action when she’s attacked by ghouls. Arucard arrives and makes short work of the fiends - and changes Seras’s life forever.
name: The Undead

deck: Alucard and Seras are sent to kill two vampire teenagers who are on a killing spree. Seras has to cope with her new life as a vampire.
description: When she joins Arucard on a hunt for a pair of murderous teenaged bloodsuckers, Seras must begin to face the harsh realities of her new existence as a vampire.
name: Club M

deck: Hellsing is investigating a microchip which, when implanted in a human, turns them into an artificial vampire. Alucard and Seras are attacked by Alexander Anderson.
description: Someone is creating artificial vampires by implanting computer chips in the brains of humans. When one goes on the attack, Seras finds herself in jeopardy - and it will be up to Arucard to save her.
name: Sword Dancer

deck: Hellsing goes after an underground group of people producing snuff films, where vampires feed on humans.
description: A disturbing snuff film has hit the streets - and its very existence could bring the Hellsing Organization tumbling down. Seras sets out on a solo mission to discover who is behind the camera.
name: Innocent as a Human

deck: The Valentine brothers attack Hellsing with an army of Ghouls.
description: Two vampire brothers boldly lead a massive mob of ghouls in an attack on Hellsing headquarters! Can Arucard and Seras prevent the swarm of armed freaks from overrunning the mansion?
name: Brotherhood

Z's Ambition! A Dark and Powerful Army!
Z's Ambition! A Great and Desperate Escape Plan!
The Beginning of The New Chapter! The Straw Hats Reunited!
An Explosive Situation! Luffy vs. Fake Luffy!
The Marines Has Set Out! The Straw Hats in Danger!
Big Guns Assembled! The Danger of the Fake Straw Hats!
The Battle is on! Show Them What You Got From Training!
Everyone Together! Luffy, Setting Out for the New World!
A Surprising Fact! The Man Who Guarded the Sunny!
Deadly Combat Under the Sea! The Demon of the Ocean Strikes!
Lost in the Deep Sea! The Straw Hats Get Separated!
Undersea Volcanic Eruption! Drifting to the Fish-Man Island!
Landing at the Fish-Man Island! Beautiful Mermaids!
Excitement Blow-out! Sanji's Life Under Threat!
The Fish-Man Island Will Be Annihilated?! Sharley's Prophecy!
The King of the Fish-Man Island! Neptune, the God of the Sea!
The Ryugu Palace! Taken by the Shark that They Saved!
A Coward and a Crybaby! The Princess in the Hard Shell Tower!
It's an Emergency! The Ryugu Place Is Occupied!
The Ryugu Palace in Shock! The Kidnapping of Shirahoshi!
Hordy's Onslaught! The Retaliatory Plan Set Into Motion!
The Battle in the Ryugu Palace! Zoro vs. Hordy!
Keep Shirahoshi Safe! Decken Close Behind!
The Straw Hats Defeated?! Hordy Gains Control of the Ryugu Palace!
The Haunting Ties! Nami and the Fish-Man Pirates!
A Hero Who Freed the Slaves! An Adventurer Tiger!
Kizaru Appears! A Trap to Catch Tiger!
A Team is Formed! Save Chopper

deck: The fight for the Hellsing mansion continues.
description: Arucard, Seras, and Walter continue their fight against the attacking Valentine brothers. Saving Hellsing HQ won’t be easy - every member of Hellsing that falls quickly rises to join the Valentines’ ghoul army!
name: Dead Zone
The Death of the Hero! A Shocking Truth of Tiger!
The Sun Pirates Split! Jimbei vs. Arlong!
Shaking Fish-Man Island! A Celestial Dragon Drifts In!
A Sudden Tragedy! A Gunshot Shuts Down the Future!
Back to the Present! Hordy Makes a Move!

deck: Integra has to deal with the loss of the majority of her soldiers. Alucard and Anderson face off again.
description: After losing so many soldiers during the Valentine brothers’ attack, Integra begins attempting to rebuild Hellsing’s forces. Meanwhile, Seras leads an assault against a vampire in the London Underground.
name: Duel
The Kingdom in Shock! An Order to Execute Neptune Issued!
A Rift Opens Up! Luffy vs. Jimbei!
Something Has Happened to Hordy! The True Power of the Evil Drug!

deck: Integra deals with the aftermath of the Valentine attack. She is forced to recruit new soldiers.
description: Hellsing investigates the origin of the computer chips being used to create artificial vampires. The process could prove difficult, due to the destruction of the factory that was producing the technology.
name: Kill House

deck: Integra is visited by her "sister." Seras, however, thinks that something is extremely wrong.
description: When Hellsing’s assault on a castle is suddenly called off by the S.A.S., Seras can’t help but think something fishy is afoot. Her suspicions grow even more with the unexpected arrival of Integra’s sister.
name: Red Rose Village

deck: Integra undergoes an emergency surgery after the injuries she sustained during her attempted assassination. She remembers the day she first met Alucard.
description: Integra is on the operating table after slicing her own throat. As she drifts in and out of consciousness, her thoughts turn to her history with Arucard and her early days with the Hellsing Organization.
name: Master of Monster

deck: Integra plans for a visit from the Queen of England.
description: After numerous attacks on the Queen’s life, Integra sets a trap at the Tower of London to catch those responsible. Meanwhile, Seras tries to understand the strange visions she’s started experiencing.
name: Transcend Force

deck: Seras and Alucard must fight a group of vampires dressed as British SAS, making the British army suspicious of Hellsing. Incognito reveals himself.
description: Hellsing is under attack from all sides at the Tower of London. Can Arucard and his allies survive while trapped between the British Army and swarms of artificial vampires?
name: Total Destruction

deck: Integra and all of Hellsing are being chased by the government. Despite that, they still need to defeat Incognito.
description: As Integra and Walter fight to escape the Tower of London, the vicious battle between Arucard and Incognito rages on - and if Arucard falls to his foe, the entire world will suffer.
name: Hellfire

deck: The Doctor and Rose go to suburbs of London, guess what? They find trouble.
name: Fear Her

name: Army of Ghosts

deck: A man becomes obsessed with The Doctor. What could possibly happen?

name: Doomsday

deck: The Daleks continue there havoc.
description: As the Daleks leave a trail of destruction through 1930's Manhattan, the Doctor and Martha are left with a new question, what is a Human-Dalek.
name: Evolution of the Daleks

deck: A science experiment gone wrong and The Doctor has to fix it up.
name: The Lazarus Experiment

deck: The Doctor has 42 minutes to save the ship from crashing into a sun.
The Doctor embraces his human side.
name: Human Nature

deck: The Doctor finds out who he is or should i say John Smith.
name: The Family of Blood

deck: Don't Blink. Whatever you do, do not blink, even for a second.
name: Blink

deck: The end of time and something isn't right.
name: Utopia

deck: DUM, DUM, DUM, DUM. The sound of the never ending drums.
name: The Sound of the Drums

deck: The Doctor Vs. The Master
name: The Last of the Time Lords

deck: Annihilus attaches a mind-control device on to Red Hulk and sends him and Skaar to attack the ship that Hulk, She-Hulk, and A-Bomb used to get into the Negative Zone.With the promise of a destroyed earth it's up to the Agents of S.M.A.S.H to stop Annihilus and a mysterious figure that lurks in the background.
name: Doorway to Destruction Part 2
